citations.desc: Cleaning, sanitization, housekeeping, and pest control.
citations.narrative:
The deck area adjacent to the outdoor housing facility has a large amount of accumulated equipment present. In addition,
several of the plastic tubs will require cleaning. Premises must be kept clean and free from accumulations of excess
equipment to facilitate pest control, and to protect the health and well-being of the animals.
To be corrected by: 6/15/2022
This inspection and exit interview were conducted with the facility representatives.
End Section
